replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"歷史Post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從中吸取 學習"},{"pid":"a04dc6a3a51d534a636237ee992adfe4c7d55ccf","tid":1508274,"uid":141508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"Kosovo比俄佬睇住，所以獨立唔晒<br />\nCatalonia歐盟同美國普遍唔支持，所以獨立唔到<br />\n台灣雖然唔受國際承認，但因為政制+地理問題，暗盤一般都會當獨立國家處理<br />\n所以只有中國內政失火，自顧不睱，西方同聯合國普遍支持，香港先有機會"},{"pid":"10968dda56333f56011830a6b133ac92b18726e8","tid":1508274,"uid":130026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04dc6a3a51d534a636237ee992adfe4c7d55ccf","tid":1508274,"uid":141508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"Kosovo比俄佬睇住，所以獨立唔晒<br />\nCatalonia歐盟同美國普遍唔支持，所以獨立唔到<br />\n台灣雖然唔受國際承認，但因為政制+地理問題，暗盤一般都會當獨立國家處理<br />\n所以只有中國內政失火，自顧不睱，西方同聯合國普遍支持，香港先有機會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"引起大中國內政失火嘅可以係發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde3dcf5856d3dcd4475700477c06931c84cdb8a","tid":1508274,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Kosovo比俄佬睇住，所以獨立唔晒</blockquote><br />\n俄軍好似撤走哂了<br />\n頂多只能o係安理會用否決權唔畀科索沃入UN<br />\n<br />\n記得當年台灣李登輝諗住用經濟援助初立國o既科索沃, 來換取建交, 銀碼都成億億聲<br />\n結果科索沃係錢照收, 但唔肯同台建交, 並話只會同UN成員建交<br />\n由於要入UN, 所以冇得唔靠蝗國"},{"pid":"fcc3c43f7761da70379da43cffb9c9dccdd96601","tid":1508274,"uid":9692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"東歐佬(計埋北歐FINLAND) 個種戰鬥格入哂血<br />\n你睇Kola&scaron;inac徙手擊退持刀匪徒就知<br />\n<br />\n香港好難同人比"},{"pid":"60eaeb266a0a68df8f1527b3a499ce89b371be46","tid":1508274,"uid":265896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"借位推一推<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v12oljF_8WE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv12oljF_8WE&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=fe1eb49e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v12oljF_8WE</a>"}]}